snippet.title: (OLD) Umami Grove - Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1394470/Umami_Grove/

*This trailer is out of date!* Please take a look at the new one: https://youtu.be/LOIwKKTA9L8

*All footage is from an early alpha build and subject to change*
Umami Grove is a relaxed, physics-based VR adventure game with a plethora of creatures to meet and places to explore. Jump, climb, duck, and swing your way though a unique cooking-themed adventure using a powerful movement and interaction system.
